  "instructions": [
    "combine ginger, galangal, lemongrass, and kaffir lime leaves in a large pot",
    "add tripe to the pot and poach for 1 hour",
    "add coconut milk, turmeric, coriander, cumin, chili flakes, salt, and black pepper to the pot",
    "stir in sugar and bring to a boil",
    "reduce heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes",
    "serve in bowls and garnish with chopped fresh cilantro",
    "serve with steamed rice or roti",
    "serve immediately and enjoy"
